{"tid":799401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[牛牛好慘]中國暴牛口蹄疫 已撲殺100頭 網傳推牛落坑活埋片段","createTime":"2018-08-30T04:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T00:49:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"924cf22332d9f1b177926063d2857919642b6982","tid":799401,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:50:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/zwitterion2018/status/1034814708052684802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzwitterion2018%2Fstatus%2F1034814708052684802&d=EYS8dUhnf9IpOxqvfzW2QwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=aee41d48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzwitterion2018%2Fstatus%2F1034814708052684802&h=261436ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/zwitterion2018/status/1034814708052684802</a><br />\n<br />\n據中共農業農村部新聞辦公室28日發布，內蒙古興和縣發生一起牛O型口蹄疫疫情，已撲殺100頭。<br />\n繼東北牛羊炭疽病以及全國各地出現的非洲豬瘟疫後，又在內蒙古草原出現了口蹄疫，看來今年的豬牛羊等肉類產品要全軍覆沒。<br />\n經濟持續惡化，物價飛漲，估計接下來能捨得吃葷的也越來越少，身在牆國，自求多福。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19083ad335ea55d85680ec52ab23ae1fe2054d5d","tid":799401,"uid":200328,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"豬瘟牛疫<br />\n下一步禽流感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8321ce0891a2e97cfb25b1f4808b5176ad788b71","tid":799401,"uid":3454,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:53:10.000Z","msg":"前幾日經過上水屠房，見到好多牛牛一車車咁送入去，有好多隻流眼淚 佢地知就快俾人殺...真係好慘!<br />\n<br />\n牛牛係有靈性，幫人耤田....請大家唔好食牛! 我都已經開始戒...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7c549565d6994941f88b87a02e5889e25f3640","tid":799401,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8